{"tid":2391068,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"因玩GME而玩美股既入一入黎","createTime":"2021-02-02T03:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T04:59:50.000Z","uid":165198,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1d92b942bc8aa6a2a62b5823f431769c6d67d646","tid":2391068,"uid":165198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:26:45.000Z","msg":"香港人好有愛心<br />\n原來都好關愛大家個荷包<br />\nanyway, 有句野叫悶聲發大財<br />\n玩得風險投資就唔會輸打嬴要<br />\n<br />\n眼見新手唔風險管理就鳩衝入場 輸錢就怨<br />\n一隻股有本事升10幾倍 跌幾倍都係好合理<br />\n輸左帳面就問溝唔溝貨 但溝黎為乜又唔知<br />\n唔係連登叫人SH既問題 而係入場基本上腦都唔用<br />\nSH原因係咩又唔知<br />\n期權係乜又唔知<br />\n大佬家陣玩緊美股唔係港股 睇多D香港以外既新聞同報導啦<br />\n<br />\n深知大家想賭一賭SS飛天<br />\n但自己衡量風險 自己參考多啲資料<br />\n家陣係你自己投資緊唔係借人把口黎投資<br />\n唔係淨係講GME AMC呢啲<br />\n而係所有投資都係同一樣心態 諗清楚先好行動<br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n本人都持有GME<br />\n大家都小心風險管理啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mmrqsqc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMmrqsqc.jpg&h=b93d555f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca2671369dff799ecc3d3d26fb3c13dad2bc2c8a","tid":2391068,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:28:09.000Z","msg":"SH就會嬴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5e07eddcdf45489d2bbead534be4809ff71967","tid":2391068,"uid":6952,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:40:04.000Z","msg":"點樣可以跌幾倍?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68627a2758e2379136a654d5c60afd6963296f74","tid":2391068,"uid":84415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:29:46.000Z","msg":"淡友block<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48053850e15671457ec01d4d2899ec6ee6c2ff0